{"type":"message","id":"c8305838","parentId":"b4b45a8b","timestamp":"2026-06-12T02:34:49.202Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can see the config is in `openclaw.json`. The skills config section is lacking. I need to add the `skills` section with the plugin-skills directory as an extra dir, and also register each individual skill entry.\n\nLet me look at how to properly add the plugin-skills directory and individual skill entries.\n\nThe skills are in `C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\plugin-skills\\`. According to the docs, I can use `skills.load.extraDirs` to add this directory.\n\nBut wait - looking more carefully, the skills from `plugin-skills/` that ARE showing up (feishu-*) are there because they come bundled with the feishu plugin. The other skills (gitlab-permission, memory-keeper, solo-config-field, tapd-bug-create, tapd-vsmode-story, update-server) need to be registered.\n\nLet me read the individual skills to understand what they do, then add them to the config.\n\nActually, let me first just check what the user is asking. They said \"你之前学会的技能怎么没有了\" which means \"How come the skills you learned before are gone?\" - they expected me to have certain skills that I no longer have. This is because the plugin skills exist on disk but aren't registered in the config.\n\nI should let the user know what I found and ask if they want me to re-register them.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"发现了！问题出在 OpenClaw 的配置里。\n\n你之前在 `C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\plugin-skills\\` 下面安装的这些自定义技能都在磁盘上没丢：\n\n1. **`gitlab-permission`** — GitLab 权限管理\n2. **`memory-keeper`** — 记忆管理\n3. **`solo-config-field`** — 配置字段管理\n4. **`tapd-bug-create`** — TAPD 创建 Bug\n5. **`tapd-vsmode-story`** — TAPD 故事管理\n6. **`update-server`** — 更新测试服 ← 这就是刚才说的那个！\n\n但配置里只配了 `skills.allowBundled: [\"skill-creator\", \"taskflow\", \"taskflow-inbox-triage\"]`，没有把这些 plugin-skills 注册进去，所以它们没有加载。\n\n需要我把它们重新注册到 `openclaw.json` 的 `skills` 配置里，然后重启生效吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1957,"output":520,"cacheRead":47872,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50349,"cost":{"input":0.00027398,"output":0.00014560000000000002,"cacheRead":0.0013404159999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0017599959999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781231683017,"responseId":"906f778c-ca6e-44f4-b85a-410b2613a0ae"}}
