{"type":"message","id":"fe6a4202","parentId":"88f2299d","timestamp":"2026-06-12T03:16:01.619Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I found some great results. Let me summarize what's available:\n\n**现成方案（直接用）：**\n\n1. **腾讯围棋APP**（最成熟）— 拍照数子功能，支持9路/13路/19路棋盘，腾讯围棋APP内置，免费\n2. **微信小程序\"拍照看围棋输赢\"** — 微信里直接搜就能用\n3. **云比赛网** — 2024年上线拍照数子功能，面向裁判和普通用户\n4. **围棋拍照数子APP（围棋计时器）** — 安卓应用\n\n**开源方案（可自建）：**\n\n1. **Kaya** (https://github.com/kaya-go/kaya) — ⭐ 最佳选择！开源，支持从照片识别棋盘（board recognition from photos），跨平台（Win/Mac/Linux/Web），带AI分析\n2. **Rocamgo** — Python+OpenCV 实现围棋棋盘识别\n3. **GBR (Go Board Recognition)** — 开源棋盘识别\n4. **img2sgf** — 图片转SGF棋谱\n5. **kifu-snap** — Remi Coulom（围棋AI专家）整理的棋盘识别工具列表\n\nLet me also quickly look at Kaya to see its details.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_yW9UCRXTo0hVxDh1eUi17777","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"url":"https://github.com/kaya-go/kaya","maxChars":5000}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_01_hMf22V86YtdTItUnmnLo2137","name":"web_fetch","arguments":{"url":"https://www.remi-coulom.fr/kifu-snap/","maxChars":5000}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2981,"output":408,"cacheRead":46848,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50237,"cost":{"input":0.00041734000000000004,"output":0.00011424,"cacheRead":0.0013117439999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001843324}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781234156485,"responseId":"8594dffb-c439-4dd4-abc8-2aa7a7056a5c"}}
