{"type":"message","id":"4fb72b49","parentId":"6dd38b58","timestamp":"2026-06-12T03:18:38.633Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK, the token has access to these repos. But not creation permission.\n\nI think the issue is that this is a fine-grained PAT that was scoped to specific repos and doesn't have \"create\" permission for new repos. The user needs to either:\n1. Create the repo manually on GitHub\n2. Or give me a classic PAT with `repo` scope\n\nActually wait, even if I can't create the repo, I can try to create it via the GitHub web interface using the cookies and Playwright... but Playwright isn't installed.\n\nLet me ask the user to either:\n1. Create the repo manually at github.com/new (name it \"OpenClaw\", public)\n2. Or provide a classic PAT with full repo scope\n\nActually, let me try another approach - maybe I can create the repo via the browser cookies using a different API call.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"这个 fine-grained PAT 没有创建仓库的权限。你能帮我做一步吗？\n\n**方式一（最快）：** 打开 https://github.com/new ，创建仓库 `OpenClaw`（Public，勾上 Add a README），然后我就能 push 上去了。\n\n**方式二：** 创建一个 **经典 token**（Classic PAT），勾上 `repo` 全部权限，粘贴给我。\n\n几分钟的事，你先忙哪个？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":138,"output":269,"cacheRead":61824,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62231,"cost":{"input":0.00001932,"output":0.00007532,"cacheRead":0.001731072,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001825712}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781234314504,"responseId":"3a8c6bf8-f982-477f-a9d1-4b16e584a84e"}}
