{"type":"message","id":"f2c1c917","parentId":"b7d17ee0","timestamp":"2026-06-12T03:36:19.971Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Repo created! Now let me:\n1. Clone it\n2. Set up the backup structure\n3. Configure git\n4. Create the backup files\n5. Push everything\n\nThe structure should be:\n```\nOpenClaw/\n├── setup.ps1              # Automated setup script for new machines\n├── README.md              # What this is\n├── skills/                # Custom skills\n│   ├── update-server/     # from plugin-skills\n│   ├── gitlab-permission/\n│   ├── memory-keeper/\n│   ├── solo-config-field/\n│   ├── tapd-bug-create/\n│   └── tapd-vsmode-story/\n├── workspace/             # Workspace files (excluding secrets)\n│   ├── AGENTS.md\n│   ├── SOUL.md\n│   ├── IDENTITY.md\n│   ├── USER.md\n│   ├── TOOLS.md\n│   └── HEARTBEAT.md\n├── memory/                # Memory files\n│   └── *.md\n├── config/                # Config template (secrets redacted)\n│   └── openclaw.json\n└── scripts/               # Utility scripts\n```\n\nLet me first clone the repo, then organize everything.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"仓库创建成功！现在来搭建备份结构。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_QYWCUmRctHMAEWxxq9Yn9638","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"$env:GIT_TERMINAL_PROMPT=0; $env:GIT_ASKPASS=\"echo\"; git clone https://yoshikun: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@github.com/yoshikun/OpenClaw.git \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\OpenClaw\" 2>&1","timeout":15}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":132,"output":437,"cacheRead":68096,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68665,"cost":{"input":0.000018480000000000003,"output":0.00012236000000000001,"cacheRead":0.001906688,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002047528}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781235375643,"responseId":"a0f6d042-d85b-4fa1-96b7-c4bc6d251116"}}
