{"type":"message","id":"ccfb8b64","parentId":"afb35998","timestamp":"2026-06-12T03:36:33.188Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now let me copy everything over. I'll do this step by step. Let me start with:\n\n1. Copy all skill files\n2. Copy workspace files (excluding secrets)\n3. Copy memory files\n4. Create config template\n5. Create setup script\n6. Create .gitignore\n7. Commit and push\n\nLet me use a comprehensive script.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_ymhNG10NUdWSWzRvOjfI6598","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\OpenClaw\\build_backup.ps1","content":"$RepoDir = \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\OpenClaw\"\n$Workspace = \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\"\n$PluginSkills = \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\plugin-skills\"\n$OpenClawDir = \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\"\n\nWrite-Host \"=== Building OpenClaw backup ===\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n\n# 1. Copy skills\nWrite-Host \"[1/6] Copying skills...\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n$skillDirs = @(\"update-server\", \"gitlab-permission\", \"memory-keeper\", \"solo-config-field\", \"tapd-bug-create\", \"tapd-vsmode-story\")\nforeach ($skill in $skillDirs) {\n    $src = Join-Path $PluginSkills $skill\n    $dst = Join-Path $RepoDir \"skills\" $skill\n    if (Test-Path $src) {\n        Copy-Item -Recurse -Force $src $dst\n        Write-Host \"  ✓ $skill\"\n    }\n}\n\n# 2. Copy workspace core files (excluding secrets and media)\nWrite-Host \"[2/6] Copying workspace files...\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n$workspaceFiles = @(\"AGENTS.md\", \"SOUL.md\", \"IDENTITY.md\", \"USER.md\", \"TOOLS.md\", \"HEARTBEAT.md\")\nforeach ($f in $workspaceFiles) {\n    $src = Join-Path $Workspace $f\n    if (Test-Path $src) {\n        Copy-Item $src (Join-Path $RepoDir \"workspace\" $f)\n        Write-Host \"  ✓ $f\"\n    }\n}\n\n# 3. Copy memory files\nWrite-Host \"[3/6] Copying memory files...\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\nif (Test-Path (Join-Path $Workspace \"memory\")) {\n    Copy-Item -Recurse -Force (Join-Path $Workspace \"memory\\*\") (Join-Path $RepoDir \"memory\\\")\n    Write-Host \"  ✓ memory files\"\n}\nif (Test-Path (Join-Path $Workspace \"MEMORY.md\")) {\n    Copy-Item (Join-Path $Workspace \"MEMORY.md\") (Join-Path $RepoDir \"memory\\MEMORY.md\")\n    Write-Host \"  ✓ MEMORY.md\"\n}\n\n# 4. Create config template (with secrets redacted)\nWrite-Host \"[4/6] Creating config template...\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n$configPath = Join-Path $OpenClawDir \"openclaw.json\"\nif (Test-Path $configPath) {\n    $config = Get-Content $configPath -Raw\n    # Redact sensitive values\n    $config = $config -replace '\"token\": \"[^\"]*\"', '\"token\": \"***redacted***\"'\n    $config = $config -replace '\"appSecret\": \"[^\"]*\"', '\"appSecret\": \"***redacted***\"'\n    $config = $config -replace '\"apiKey\": \"[^\"]*\"', '\"apiKey\": \"***redacted***\"'\n    # Save redacted config\n    $config | Out-File (Join-Path $RepoDir \"config\\openclaw.json\") -Encoding utf8\n    Write-Host \"  ✓ config template created (secrets redacted)\"\n}\n\n# Also save the gitignore for credential files\n@\"\n# Secrets\n*.cookies.json\n*_cookies.json\n*_csrf.json\n*token*\n\n# Media\nmedia/\ninbound/\n\n# OS\n.DS_Store\nThumbs.db\n\n# Node\nnode_modules/\n\"@ | Out-File (Join-Path $RepoDir \".gitignore\") -Encoding utf8\nWrite-Host \"  ✓ .gitignore created\"\n\nWrite-Host \"[5/6] Backup complete!\" -ForegroundColor Green\nWrite-Host \"[6/6] Ready to commit and push\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":305,"output":1035,"cacheRead":68992,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":70332,"cost":{"input":0.0000427,"output":0.0002898,"cacheRead":0.0019317759999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002264276}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781235384922,"responseId":"1a8c45c0-6e81-4364-a6a1-b4c765a5157