{"type":"message","id":"ed848d64","parentId":"9f471524","timestamp":"2026-06-12T03:37:40.335Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"200! The repo is on GitHub and accessible. Let me also clean up temp files and update memory.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"搞定了！仓库已经 push 成功 ✅\n\n来看看你 GitHub 上的成果：**[github.com/yoshikun/OpenClaw](https://github.com/yoshikun/OpenClaw)**\n\n### 备份了什么\n\n| 目录 | 内容 |\n|------|------|\n| `skills/` | 6 个自定义技能（update-server, gitlab-permission, memory-keeper, solo-config-field, tapd-bug-create, tapd-vsmode-story） |\n| `workspace/` | AGENTS.md, SOUL.md, IDENTITY.md, USER.md, TOOLS.md, HEARTBEAT.md |\n| `config/openclaw.json` | 配置模板（敏感信息已脱敏） |\n| `setup.ps1` | **一键部署脚本** → 在新电脑上跑这个就能恢复 |\n| `README.md` | 详细说明 |\n\n### 新电脑上复刻只需要\n\n```powershell\ngit clone https://github.com/yoshikun/OpenClaw.git\ncd OpenClaw\npowershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File setup.ps1\n```\n\n然后把你的 API Key 和 token 填进 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`，重启 Gateway 就完事了。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":29,"output":288,"cacheRead":91520,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91837,"cost":{"input":0.00000406,"output":0.00008064,"cacheRead":0.0025625599999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00264726}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781235456774,"responseId":"84214641-8270-4d85-9cbd-be053e2f9f4f"}}
