{"type":"message","id":"8eb332f1","parentId":"57323155","timestamp":"2026-06-12T03:50:56.438Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, now the upstream is set. \"Everything up-to-date\" confirms it works. Now let me add the cron job.\n\nFor the cron job, I need to:\n1. Create a cron that runs daily (e.g., at 2:00 AM when nobody is using it)\n2. Use `isolated` session\n3. Have it run the backup script\n4. Optionally tell the user the result\n\nWait, the cron job runs an agent turn, not a shell script. So I should either:\n- Have the cron job send a message to me to do the backup\n- OR use the cron job with an isolated agent run and have the agent run the backup\n\nActually, looking at the cron docs more carefully, `isolated` mode runs a dedicated agent turn. So the message/prompt would be interpreted by the agent. But I need to run a PowerShell script, not a chat interaction.\n\nThe better approach might be to:\n1. Use the exec tool within the cron job's agent turn to run the backup script\n2. Or have the cron tell the main session agent to run the backup\n\nActually, the simplest approach is to create a cron job that says \"Run the daily backup - execute the backup script and report results\" - the agent will understand to use the exec tool to run the script.\n\nLet me create the cron job.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Now let me set up the cron job for daily backup."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_f5rJzIuNUB3iIO9JcA638656","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw cron add `\n  --name \"Daily OpenClaw Backup\" `\n  --cron \"0 2 * * *\" `\n  --tz \"Asia/Shanghai\" `\n  --session isolated `\n  --message \"Run the daily OpenClaw backup. Execute PowerShell script at: C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\OpenClaw\\daily_backup.ps1 -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File, then report the result.\" `\n  --announce `\n  --channel feishu `\n  --to \"user:ou_6509d346e8d50ef882f89c436e6c977f\" 2>&1","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":228,"output":496,"cacheRead":100608,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":101332,"cost":{"input":0.00003192,"output":0.00013888,"cacheRead":0.002817024,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002987824}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781236250954,"responseId":"75afafe2-0947-4436-a193-b27dbbcac5b7"}}
