{"type":"message","id":"1105edd5","parentId":"0f291eae","timestamp":"2026-06-12T03:51:25.906Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can see the cron job was added successfully - there are now 3 jobs and the 3rd one is \"OpenClaw Daily Backup\" with schedule \"0 2 * * *\" and enabled=true. The ConvertFrom-Json error is just because of the Chinese characters in the existing jobs, not an issue with my job.\n\nThe setup is complete. Let me clean up the temp files and update memory.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"搞定了！每天凌晨 **2:00** 自动备份已就绪 ✅\n\n### 备份机制\n\n```\n每天 2:00 AM (北京时间)\n    ↓\nCron 触发 → 运行 daily_backup.ps1\n    ↓\n同步 workspace/*.md → repo\n同步 memory/*.md → repo\n同步 skills/**/SKILL.md → repo\n    ↓\ngit commit + push\n    ↓\n有变化 → 自动 push\n无变化 → 静默跳过\n```\n\n### 备份了什么\n\n- **workspace/**: AGENTS.md, SOUL.md, TOOLS.md, HEARTBEAT.md 等\n- **memory/**: 所有每日日志文件\n- **skills/**: 技能 SKILL.md\n- **config/**: 配置模板\n\nCredential 已用 git store 保存，无需每次输密码。出错了 agent 会检查错误码，只有异常时才通知你 —— 平时静默就好，不打扰睡觉 😎"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1528,"output":295,"cacheRead":104320,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":106143,"cost":{"input":0.00021392,"output":0.0000826,"cacheRead":0.00292096,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00321748}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781236281287,"responseId":"c3790c6b-b654-452e-9473-28bd2ce68daf"}}
